    <item>
      <title>Primark 圣诞销售强劲，购物者寻求廉价时尚</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-01-23/primark-christmas-sales-strong-as-shoppers-seek-budget-fashion</link>
      <description><![CDATA[廉价时装零售商 Primark 在圣诞节临近时销售强劲，因为在持续高通胀的情况下，资金短缺的英国购物者专注于降价服装。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-01-23/primark-christmas-sales-strong-as-shoppers-seek-budget-fashion</guid>
      <pubDate>Tue, 23 Jan 2024 07:16:50 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>比亚迪超越大众成为2023年中国销量第一汽车品牌</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-01-23/byd-crowned-china-s-no-1-selling-car-brand-for-2023-over-vw</link>
      <description><![CDATA[比亚迪公司将于 2023 年正式超越大众汽车公司，成为中国最畅销的汽车品牌，这清楚地表明其在全球最大汽车市场上对电动汽车的全力押注正在获得回报，并帮助其超越了一些全球最大的传统品牌。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-01-23/byd-crowned-china-s-no-1-selling-car-brand-for-2023-over-vw</guid>
      <pubDate>Tue, 23 Jan 2024 07:14:55 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>丰田董事长预测纯电动汽车市场份额将仅达到 30%</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-01-23/toyota-chairman-predicts-battery-electric-cars-will-only-reach-30-share</link>
      <description><![CDATA[丰田汽车公司董事长丰田章男认为，纯电动汽车最多将占据 30% 的市场份额，其余部分则由混合动力汽车、氢燃料电池汽车和燃油汽车占据。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-01-23/toyota-chairman-predicts-battery-electric-cars-will-only-reach-30-share</guid>
      <pubDate>Tue, 23 Jan 2024 07:04:50 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>法郎强劲削弱业绩，斯沃琪集团销售额未能创下历史新高</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-01-23/swatch-group-sales-miss-record-as-china-rebound-lags</link>
      <description><![CDATA[2023 年 3 月 7 日星期二，一位顾客在日本东京举行的发布会上购买了 Swatch AG Mission to Moonshine Gold MoonSwatch。Swatch 发布了带有金色秒针的新版 MoonSwatch，这是广受欢迎的合作款的最新版本其高端欧米茄品牌和入门级斯沃琪品牌之间的关系。摄影师：Kiyoshi Ota/彭博社]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-01-23/swatch-group-sales-miss-record-as-china-rebound-lags</guid>
      <pubDate>Tue, 23 Jan 2024 06:25:45 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>索尼放弃 100 亿美元的印度合并后，Zee 股价暴跌 30%</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-01-23/zee-slumps-10-after-sony-scraps-10-billion-india-merger</link>
      <description><![CDATA[Zee Entertainment Enterprises Ltd. 取消了与索尼集团公司 (Sony Group Corp.) 的 100 亿美元合并计划，引发了一系列评级下调，分析师预测这家印度公司的估值将大幅缩水，此后该公司股价创下五年来最大跌幅。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-01-23/zee-slumps-10-after-sony-scraps-10-billion-india-merger</guid>
      <pubDate>Tue, 23 Jan 2024 03:56:31 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>日本央行上田认为前景更加确定，日元恢复上涨</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-01-23/yen-extends-decline-slightly-after-boj-keeps-policy-unchanged</link>
      <description><![CDATA[日本央行行长上田一夫表示，前景的确定性正在逐渐增强，日元摆脱了最初的波动并上涨。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-01-23/yen-extends-decline-slightly-after-boj-keeps-policy-unchanged</guid>
      <pubDate>Tue, 23 Jan 2024 03:19:51 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>随着美国再次打击胡塞武装，布伦特原油价格保持在 80 美元上方</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-01-23/latest-oil-market-news-and-analysis-for-january-23</link>
      <description><![CDATA[在美国和英国对伊朗支持的也门胡塞叛乱分子进行新一轮打击后，油价保持上涨，加剧了中东紧张局势，抵消了对全球供应仍然充足的担忧。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-01-23/latest-oil-market-news-and-analysis-for-january-23</guid>
      <pubDate>Tue, 23 Jan 2024 00:12:15 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
